## Proposed Changes

The project will be organized into a `backend` folder (FastAPI) and a `frontend` folder (React + Vite + Tailwind CSS).

### Backend (Python + FastAPI)

Create a FastAPI application in the workspace under a `backend` folder.

#### [NEW] [backend/requirements.txt](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/requirements.txt)
Lists all Python packages:
- `fastapi`, `uvicorn` (core API layer)
- `mysql-connector-python`, `sqlalchemy` (MySQL connection & ORM)
- `qdrant-client` (vector database client running in local disk mode)
- `pymupdf` (PDF extraction)
- `pytesseract`, `pillow` (OCR fallback for scanned PDFs)
- `google-generativeai` (Gemini model interface for embeddings and chat generation)
- `python-multipart` (handles PDF file uploads)
- `python-dotenv` (loads env variables)
- `pydantic` (validation)
- `websockets` (for voice streaming if applicable)

#### [NEW] [backend/.env](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/.env)
Contains server configurations:
```ini
PORT=8000
DATABASE_URL=mysql+mysqlconnector://root:password@localhost:3306/pdf_assistant_db
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key
QDRANT_PATH=./qdrant_db
