```

#### [NEW] [backend/database.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/database.py)
Initializes SQLAlchemy engine for MySQL. Sets up session maker and base model class. Creates tables on startup if they don't exist.

#### [NEW] [backend/models.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/models.py)
Defines relational DB models storing metadata:
- `Document`: File name, page count, file path, upload time.
- `Message`: Chat history (sender: user/bot, query text, audio paths, timestamp, citations, conversation ID).

#### [NEW] [backend/services/pdf_processor.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/services/pdf_processor.py)
Extracts contents and handles indexing:
- PyMuPDF text reader: Extracts text page-by-page.
- OCR checks: If a page contains zero text, performs Tesseract OCR on page image snapshot.
- Chunking helper: Recursively splits text into overlap chunks of ~500 characters, tagging each chunk with `doc_id`, `doc_name`, and `page_number`.

#### [NEW] [backend/services/vector_store.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/services/vector_store.py)
Qdrant integration service:
- Initializes `QdrantClient(path=QDRANT_PATH)` for local serverless vector persistence on disk.
- Creates a collection `"pdf_chunks"` with vector size `768` (matching Gemini `text-embedding-004`).
- Computes Gemini embeddings of text chunks on document upload and upserts them.
- Performs cosine semantic search for a given question embedding and returns top hits with page numbers and names.

#### [NEW] [backend/services/chat_rag.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/services/chat_rag.py)
RAG Logic Service:
- Summarizes context, builds history, prompts Gemini 1.5/2.5 Flash.
- Ensures the model answers *only* from PDF context.
- Formats final response with citations (page numbers, matching text snippet, document name).

#### [NEW] [backend/main.py](file:///d:/ai%20powered%20pdf%20assisstant/backend/main.py)
Exposes FastAPI API endpoints:
- `POST /upload`: Save PDF to disk, run background task for text extraction & Qdrant indexing.
- `POST /chat`: Query endpoint. Takes current question, language ("en"/"hi"), conversation history, returns text response and source citations.
- `GET /documents`: Return list of uploaded PDFs with metadata.
- `DELETE /documents/{doc_id}`: Removes PDF from local space and deletes chunks from Qdrant vector database.
- `GET /history`: Returns chat history.

